
Geo ARRAS
First Commit - V 0.1
Demo - http://geodeal.in
Geo arras is a wordpress (http://wordpress.org) theme based on arras (www.arrastheme.com)
The theme uses Geo Mashup Plugin to display the stores on a google map.
The location is generated based on Regions.
Custom CSS can be used.

Features
- Custom Post type 'stores'
- Custom Taxonomy 'Regions'
- Support for 'Facebook Comments'
- Custom Login Page with Custom Logo


Theme CSS - GEOAPP.CSS



